      * L11: 001100     ACCEPT X.
      * L12: 001200     ACCEPT Y.
      * L13: 001300     IF (X > 100)
      * L14: 001400         COMPUTE Z = X + Y.
      * L15: 001500         DISPLAY Z.
      * L16: 001600     STOP RUN.
